{"tid":2424684,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中環在線：張華峰似小精靈吉利蛋 - 李華華","createTime":"2021-02-26T18:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T07:05:18.000Z","uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"87d90679cb04bebee2036f53e1c55e793cfbe01e","tid":2424684,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KWDj0-buyiVjsWCVluOYg6YGE9g=/737x491/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DT6SJA2ZP34AHHOUNIYFL6YAEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKWDj0-buyiVjsWCVluOYg6YGE9g%3D%2F737x491%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDT6SJA2ZP34AHHOUNIYFL6YAEU.jpg&h=6a04c61c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中環在線：<br />\n張華峰似小精靈吉利蛋 - 李華華<br />\n<br />\n更新時間&nbsp;(HKT):&nbsp;2016.07.29 05:20<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n張華峰同Pok&eacute;mon裏面隻吉利蛋都幾似，塊面一樣圓碌碌。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n作者 :&nbsp;李華華<br />\n<br />\nAAA<br />\n<br />\n《Pok&eacute;mon GO》玩咗成個禮拜，立法會金融服務界議員張華峰終於被玩埋一份，睇佢表情唔多自然咁，被迫同兩隻小精靈巨鉗蟹同金魚王影相，佢將相po上facebook，不過留言叫人唔好問佢個game點玩，只係問AR技術應用喺炒股會點。<br />\n望真啲，張華峰同小精靈吉利蛋有幾分似，圓碌碌，一樣咁可愛囉。不過話時話，張華峰噚日先至po小精靈相，好似有啲out，華華玩咗兩日已經冇玩。"},{"pid":"8622ba8ae1787d4014198d81275ff564e3c362ae","tid":2424684,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}